{"word":"Λιβυστικόν","slug":"Λιβυστικόν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n63068\" key=\"*libustiko/n\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Λῐβυστικόν</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, a herb, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.267</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.62</biblScope> </bibl>:—also <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Λῐβυστιάς</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">άδος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Androm.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.40</biblScope> </bibl>:—hence <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Λῐβυστικᾶτον</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, a drink made from it, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0744.tlg001:8:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Alex.Trall.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">8.2</biblScope></bibl>. [Identical with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Λιγυστικόν</foreign>, q.v.]</entryFree>"}]}